title: Rana Tanvir Hussain calls on PM Shehbaz Sharif
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jun 21 (APP): Minister for Industries and Production Rana Tanvir Hussain Friday called on Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif at the PM House.
In the meeting, they discussed the overall political situation of the country.
Member of National Assembly Dr. Shazra Mansab was also present in the meeting.
